Package: ovom3u
Version: :VERSION
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: :ARCHITECTURE
Depends: libatk1.0-0 (>= 1.12.4), libc6 (>= 2.34), libcairo2 (>= 1.2.4), libdbus-1-3 (>= 1.9.14), libdbus-glib-1-2 (>= 0.78), libgdk-pixbuf-2.0-0 (>= 2.22.0), libgl1, libglib2.0-0 (>= 2.12.0), libgtk2.0-0 (>= 2.24.0), libpango-1.0-0 (>= 1.18.0), libx11-6, libxtst6, libsqlite3-0, libmpv
Installed-Size: :INSTALLEDSIZE
Maintainer: Marco Caselli <marcocas@gmail.com>
Description: IPTV player
  OvoM3U is a simple but complete IPTV player. It use libMPV engine for playing and OpenGl for rendering, allowing for hardware accelerated playback.
 .
 Features:
   * Handle M3U lists, both local or remote
   * Full EPG Supported
   * Auto update lists or EPG from the web
   * Support CEC standard (control player from TV remote through HDMI). Need hardware support, Raspberry Pi has it.
 .
 